k'><img alt="67㎡老破小改造后，也可以有150㎡的视觉体验感" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdaf2183cd3f9123.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/>主卧灰与白营造出静谧的睡眠氛围，<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/chuanglei/" target="_blank">床</a>头处理的简洁利落，窗台的处理兼顾了晾晒和阅读的功能性。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmvwr08/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="67㎡老破小改造后，也可以有150㎡的视觉体验感" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdaf21863b9b424.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmvwr08/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="67㎡老破小改造后，也可以有150㎡的视觉体验感" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdaf2186a014646.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmvwr08/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="67㎡老破小改造后，也可以有150㎡的视觉体验感" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdaf21872ba62012.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmvwr08/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="67㎡老破小改造后，也可以有150㎡的视觉体验感" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdaf2189e5859528.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/><br/>儿童房概念原型来自帐篷，用<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/91517/" data-brandid="91517" target="_blank">现代</a>手法诠释，整个空间做抬高处理，仪式感油然而生。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmvwr08/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="67㎡老破小改造后，也可以有150㎡的视觉体验感" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202012/17/5fdaf218ab2352885.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmvwr08/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="67㎡老破小改造后，也可以有150㎡的视觉体验感" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdaf218c5deb6649.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/>卫生间隐形到底，洁净清爽。水磨石和大理石碰撞，呈现出不同的质感和肌理。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmvwr08/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="67㎡老破小改造后，也可以有150㎡的视觉体验感" src=