x+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0b8dcf13e1231.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0b8e6b16d1547.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>           耳罩里侧面有个椭圆形的光线传感器谨防耳垫放错</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/16/5fda0bbfd784d2791.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0bbc4b1e16978.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">       <strong>    光线传感在耳垫对应的孔道，这样就不会放错。</strong><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0bc003eef5375.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_17/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0bc200a2e2189.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_18/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0bc231f9c1428.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_19/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/16/5fda0bd673c356068.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">           <strong>圆钮有音量调节、播放开始、暂停、接听电话、呼叫Siri的功能。另个一个按钮是降噪、通透模式切换用的。</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_20/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0b933e87c4828.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">         <strong>  因为这个免费镌刻，使我提前收到了耳机。</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_21/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0b924a1d69749.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">           <strong>底部是充电口和6六个外向式<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/maikefeng/" target="_blank">麦克风</a></strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_22/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0b93c75326761.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_23/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0b79520654237.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">         <strong> 耳机套，很简洁，翻盖儿带磁吸</strong><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_24/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0bd356025424.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_25/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0bd2cae427754.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_26/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0bd836edc6440.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">         <strong>  苹果耳机和大法家xm3的同框图</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_27/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0bd7e03c72216.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><h2 id="cl_2">使用感受 <br/></h2><p itemprop="description"><strong>1，主动降噪，搭配了通透模式；空间音频设置，让人置身剧场中体会环绕音效；</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>2，不锈钢框架外包裹透气织物，有效的散热、分散重量，减轻头部的压迫、提高了舒适度；</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>3，伸缩套杆能稳定在想要的位置，与头部始终紧密贴合；</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>4，阳极氧化铝金属耳罩提升耳机的颜值，平衡耳朵承受的压力；</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>5，数码旋钮，能精确调节音量、暂停播放跳转音乐、接听电话和呼唤 Siri；</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>6，六个外向式麦克风检测环境噪声，传输我通话的声音，领导可以清晰地听到我的声音；</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>7，AirPods Max 的两个耳罩都配备了 Apple H1芯片，加上特制的声学设计和先进的软件，让我听歌、看电影都有身临其境的感觉。</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>8，无缝接力功能，可以在同一个icloud下的iPhone、iPad 和 Mac 之间流畅切换音频；</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>9，头戴检测功能，可以在摘掉耳机的同时，音乐电影同时暂停；当再次佩戴后可以从暂停的位置继续播放，再也不用手动操作了。</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>10，智能耳机套，AirPods Max 就会进入超低能耗状态，节省电量。</strong></p><h2 id="cl_3">总结</h2><p itemprop="description">   <strong>优点：颜值高，无苹果LOGO，可以低调的装13；摘戴耳机不用手动操作音乐电影的播放暂停；主动降噪+通透模式可以应用于很多场景；记忆海绵<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/ersai/" target="_blank">耳塞</a>让耳朵没有压迫感；配对简单，从耳机套拿出来贴近<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/zhinengshouji/" target="_blank">手机</a>（需是最新系统版本）即可自动匹配，简单易操作。</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>   缺点：首先是贵，真是贵呀，购买4个特价的大法XM3了；其次因为不锈钢的材质，有些沉；最后铝金属耳罩夏天估计会烫手，冬天是一定会冰手的。</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>   来张全家福，少了一个手机和20W快充头在领导娘家。</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785lm2d/pic_28/' target='_blank'><img alt="挎包？眼罩？实际上是AirPods Max+耳机套^_^" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fda0b792bf3c1241.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/>
